QuestData.Title: WANTED: Kil'uun
QuestData.Description: It's that damned bird!$B$BEvery few hours, this blasted thing flies right past here, and none of these idiots will stop it.$B$B"It's got the crazy in its eyes," they tell me. Pah!$B$BCommander, this bird will be the end of me. If you see it, could you cut off its stupid head and give it to me?$B$BIt'd make me feel better.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring Kil'uun's Beak to Beastmaster Tagh.
